{
  "stem": "21978.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They came to us, and they told us if you have something, watch or some valuables, give it to me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You won't need it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It will be taken away from you, but I can help you somehow later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sure that they did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I didn't see anybody, because I was-- I was jumping out and not looking back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there were people who died during the journey.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they  were just thrown out of the truck then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When we came on the platform, we were told-- it was shouted.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were shouted at.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Men and women had to be separated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't even have a chance to say goodbye to my husband, because he was sent to one side and I and my sister to other side-- women with children, older people to one side.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have been-- as a matter of fact, we were sent to a Familienlager-- family lager-- family lager, which was called B II B-- It was Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we have been sent there, because the previous transport was sent there, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know what the reason was that the people from previous transport were kept there before we came.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But after we came, the people from the first transport, which we escaped then, were sent to gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Or some of them were sent to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We met only a couple of people who were saved from the previous transport.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because we were in the Familienlager.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Later, Annetta and I, we were selected as twins.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Mengele, Hauptsturmfuhrer Mengele, was a doctor in Auschwitz, whose privilege was to use human beings as Guinea pigs for experiments.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And from every transport, there was selection done for twins.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Dwarfs were selected, there were dwarfs coming also.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
